original_title: Put Your Hands Up! - The Tribute Concert To Chuck Brown
overview: An exciting tribute concert to Go-Go music great Chuck Brown. A host of Go-Go music legends and artists join Chuck Brown in a celebration of the time-honored genre through music and song. Top recording acts such as E.U., Sugar Bear, JuJu, Back Yard, 911, Little Benny, Big Tony, and Go-Go- Mickey are all featured.
title: Put Your Hands Up! - The Tribute Concert To Chuck Brown
